name: Coldfuse - Matte Black - Prizm Black Lens Sunglasses

features: DESIGN: A lifestyle sunglass with a distinct aesthetic that features 24 components held together by a single design feature
FRAME MATERIAL: Progressive construction with lightweight titanium and the durability of O Matter™ to add depth and dimension to the style
PRIZM™ LENS TECHNOLOGY: Available with Prizm™ lenses that are designed to enhance color, contrast and detail to make the most of any activity
FIT: Three-point fit is designed for comfort and to hold your eyewear in precise optical alignment, with added adjustable silicone nosepads for the ultimate fit
